  missionState: 2
  startDelay: 5
  dialogueSequence:
  - text: I didn't knew who brought me here.
    duration: 3
  - text: No memories. Just the taste of salt and bad decisions.
    duration: 5
  - text: At the center of the island, there was a bar.
    duration: 4
  - text: There's always a bar when something's gone wrong.
    duration: 5
  - text: Smoke rising into the night... like a signal for the damned.
    duration: 6
